      <title>吉拉德称魁北克赤字将在五年内“恢复平衡”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/quebec-deficit-back-to-balance-in-five-years-says-girard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克财政部长埃里克·吉拉德列举了造成该省赤字的五大因素，并表示“赤字超出了我们的预期”。吉拉德周三在纽约彭博加拿大金融会议上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/quebec-deficit-back-to-balance-in-five-years-says-girard</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 15:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利首席执行官表示交易主管正在退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/morgan-stanley-ceo-says-trading-leaders-are-pulling-away-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席执行官泰德·皮克表示，最大的交易公司正在拉开与小型竞争对手的距离。在该公司公布第三季度华尔街最佳交易收益后，他与索纳利·巴萨克在“彭博未平仓合约”节目中进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/morgan-stanley-ceo-says-trading-leaders-are-pulling-away-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 15:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称执政期间没有出现通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/trump-claims-no-inflation-during-administration-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社权力平衡联合主持人凯莉·莱因茨 (Kailey Leinz) 对特朗普的说法进行了事实核查，特朗普称其总统任期没有带来通胀影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/trump-claims-no-inflation-during-administration-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士政府提议提高销售税以资助养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/swiss-government-proposes-raising-sales-tax-to-finance-pensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士提议自2026年起将销售税提高0.7个百分点，以帮助资助养老金支付，同时还决定削减境外购物的免税进口限额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/swiss-government-proposes-raising-sales-tax-to-finance-pensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油交易商为何对 2025 年如此悲观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/why-oil-traders-have-become-so-pessimistic-about-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中东局势动荡，油价动荡，但许多交易员对明年的市场前景仍然持坚定悲观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/why-oil-traders-have-become-so-pessimistic-about-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家马里恩表示，加拿大央行年底前可能实施两次大规模降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/two-jumbo-boc-cuts-likely-by-year-end-economist-marion-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大国家银行首席经济学家 Stefane Marion 预计，加拿大央行将在今年年底前将利率下调整整一个百分点。Marion 说：“我们都知道中性利率接近 3%，你必须尽快达到 3%。”Marion 周三在纽约彭博加拿大金融会议上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/two-jumbo-boc-cuts-likely-by-year-end-economist-marion-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金融时报报道 Advent 准备收购泰莱公司，泰莱股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/advent-is-preparing-bid-for-tate-lyle-ft-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国《金融时报》报道收购集团 Advent International 正准备提出收购要约后，配料公司 Tate &amp; Lyle Plc 股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/advent-is-preparing-bid-for-tate-lyle-ft-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 13:46:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市止跌，不受 LVMH 和 ASML 股价下跌影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/european-stocks-fall-as-lvmh-sales-drop-adds-to-asml-order-gloom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周三下午持稳，投资者权衡奢侈品巨头路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 销售额意外下滑，以及芯片设备制造商阿斯麦控股 (ASML Holding NV) 意外的疲弱前景引发的负面情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/european-stocks-fall-as-lvmh-sales-drop-adds-to-asml-order-gloom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 07:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在 70 美元附近波动，关注中东供应风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/crude-oil-advances-with-middle-east-risks-and-china-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员继续关注明年的前景和中东局势升级的风险，油价在周二暴跌后在每桶 70 美元左右波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/crude-oil-advances-with-middle-east-risks-and-china-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 23:34:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥学校闹剧让信用评估人员警惕风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/chicago-schools-drama-catches-eye-of-credit-ratings-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会领导层的突然更迭引起了穆迪评级的注意，该公司表示，在学区面临越来越大的财务挑战之际，分析师正在关注这一情况。]]></description>
